rows.label: qst101411_msg0001
rows.name:
You've returned! What of the
investigation party...?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0002
rows.name:
The Rampaging Sauros?! Such a
monster inhabited this place...?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0003
rows.name: Everyone is... I see...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0004
rows.name:
Could you tell me in detail
where the four of them are?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0005
rows.name: Thank you.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0006
rows.name:
The Volff probably won't return
to the place where their comrades
were sacrificed anytime soon.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0007
rows.name:
And if the Rampaging Sauros has
been eliminated, the threat in
the area should have decreased.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0008
rows.name:
I think I'll go to them
and pay my respects.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0009
rows.name:
And I'd like to give something to
their families as a memento...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0010
rows.name: Thank you for your cooperation!

rows.label: qst101411_msg0101
rows.name:
You've returned! What of the
investigation party...?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0102
rows.name:
The Rampaging Sauros?! Such a
monster inhabits this place...?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0103
rows.name: Everyone is... I see...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0104
rows.name:
I'd like to go and pay my
respects to the four of them...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0105
rows.name:
but it would be dangerous
if the Rampaging Sauros is
still in the vicinity.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0106
rows.name:
The Rampaging Sauros...
Come to think of it.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0107
rows.name:
There's a researcher named Tishek in
the Beraf Industrial District of the
Superbian capital, Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0108
rows.name:
I recall him presenting research
related to the Rampaging Sauros.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0109
rows.name:
You might be able to get some
clues on how to defeat it.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0110
rows.name:
I'm sorry that this isn't
certain information...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0111
rows.name: I ask for your continued cooperation.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0201
rows.name:
Please try to meet Tishek in the
Beraf Industrial District of the
Superbian capital, Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0202
rows.name:
I hope you can get some clues
that will help in defeating
the Rampaging Sauros...
